      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   b-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgr"
                                         using b                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se errori : uscita                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
