      *                  * Intestazione se carta vidimata              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Avanzamento pagina                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "PA"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     move   "#"           to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int
                     go to  int-pag-sta-999.
